oracle.apps.fnd.applseed.rt.loader.util
Class SDRowMatchUtil

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applseed.rt.loader.util.SDRowMatchUtil

public class SDRowMatchUtil
extends java.lang.Object

Utility methods for row matching for incremental loading. Incremental load can be performed by static checksums in the file, dynamic created checksums, or attribure by attribute comparison between file and database row data.
